		   Xtwitter - twitter client for X

Xtwitter is very tiny twitter client for X Window System.
It'll works on Linux, and other UNIX-like operating systems.

* Requirements

  X.org
  Imlib
  libcurl
  libxml 2.0
  glib 2.0

* Build

  % ./configure && make

* Configration

  % mkdir ~/.xtwitter
  % cat > ~/.xtwitter/config
  user=test
  pass=xxxxxxxx
  ^D

